text: The Evan Quah's banded bent-toed gecko (Cyrtodactylus evanquahi) is a species of gecko endemic to Malaysia. ==References== * http://reptile- database.reptarium.cz/species?genus=Cyrtodactylus&species;=evanquahi Category:Reptiles of Malaysia Category:Cyrtodactylus Category:Reptiles described in 2020 Category:Taxa named by Perry L.
